## Certificates API 

K8s allows you to configure these external sources:
    Static token file 
    Certificates
    3rd party identity service 

    You have to manage all these 3 above yourself 

Configure User authentication 
    Using client Certificates

Review TLS Certificates notes 

Process of certificate signing 
    1. Create key-pair - need signed by k8s CA 
    2. Generate certificate signing request (CSR)
    3. Send CRS using k8s certificates API 
    4. K8s signs certificate for you 
    5. K8s admin approves certificate 
    